Name: intrahepatic bile duct cystadenoma
Definition: An astrocytoma that is characterized as a low grade astrocytoma and has_material_basis_in neoplastic astrocytes.
Synonym: Cystadenoma of the Intrahepatic bile duct

Name: extrahepatic bile duct cystadenoma
Definition: A vaginal adenoma that is a polyp that resembles colorectal tubulovillous adenoma.
Synonym: Cystadenoma of the extrahepatic bile duct
